headline: Essex Property Trust Publishes 2024 Sustainability and Impact Report
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., June 26, 2025--Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) published today its 2024 Sustainability and Impact Report. This report recognizes the Company’s progress towards its sustainability goals and announces new emissions reduction targets, which were recently approved by the Science Based Targets initiative ("SBTi").
